title: Notice Was Returned To USCIS Because The Post Office Could Not Deliver It
body: On May 5, 2021, the Post Office returned a notice we sent you for your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190141836, because they could not deliver it. This could have a serious effect on your case. Please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request a copy of the notice immediately.
